{"tid":1852301,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求關注EX384飛往香港航機。機上有大陸人食左退燒藥。咳嗽","createTime":"2020-01-30T11:15:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-31T08:39:08.000Z","uid":153678,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1f8cbbf9f17c2cd889e263f16ee97fb20b8af809","tid":1852301,"uid":153678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:15:43.000Z","msg":"求關注: 阿聯酋EK384於30/1/2020 由曼谷飛香港將於同日17:40抵港。<br />\n情況係有唔少嘅乘客見到喺閘口入邊，有一批大陸旅行團嘅乘客佢哋不斷咳嗽，另外再加有人要瞓低未清楚係咪發燒，喺詢問之下，有一位團友承認當中有兩至三位團友有發燒症狀及咳嗽，而呢件事俾我哋部份香港乘客見得到，並已向航空公司作出投訴要求佢停止俾啲呢批乘客登機。<br />\n<br />\n直至航班離開之前大概有60至70位乘客拒絕登機，要求飛機放下行李，比我們換另一部飛機，但航空公司以冇呢一個檢疫程序拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n根據其他乘客所見所聞當中有湖北人￼<br />\n<br />\nEK態度十分差，地勤職員嘗試作勢做動作威嚇乘客￼<br />\n<br />\n利申: 本人係其中一位冇上機的乘客"},{"pid":"a3ab46cbbeffdcf1915e8f18bc77da16e47ea508","tid":1852301,"uid":246158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:19:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2886b4d638c5c409132a01dd9beb10d232a6552c","tid":1852301,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73dfde2c08ee6d1cd78d6a2779de1ee6c00bab08","tid":1852301,"uid":228475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:23:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a25953b90dc24fb86d995bf3e404ef93018e8eb2","tid":1852301,"uid":140924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:23:47.000Z","msg":"投訴EK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c72ea04ba2621d9a676d28da71d7557d7202373","tid":1852301,"uid":123933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:26:26.000Z","msg":"pu sh"},{"pid":"fa126b2caeff9035069c689aca01f59f838bd70b","tid":1852301,"uid":123696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T11:2